CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1946, pg. 9, reads: "Throngs Expected at Beauty Shop Owners' Revue - Last Call for Glamour!  April 9 is the date set for the annual Beauty Shop Owners' Association fashion revue at Schenley High School and all the lovely ladies and kiddies above will appear in the the show which promises to be the best yet... Last picture: Helen Stout, Sally Jackson and Doris Harper. - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Helen Stout, Sally Jackson and Doris Harper posed in front of Westinghouse Monument, Schenley Park
